以連登唔會上到大台，太多自以為是嘅傻仔圍住打飛機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:52:11.000Z","msg":"補充下<br />\n<br />\n其實連登都係個討論區，有乜唔太知想了解多d嘅當然會上黎問一問，唔想答咪唔好答，比有心嘅人答、無必要屌黎屌去"},{"pid":"4e8181bb12290ed16bdebe2f80b74fee1ae5ae2e","tid":1722420,"uid":59794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:53:12.000Z","msg":"6月嗰陣話唔割就唔割<br />\n唔該其他冷氣軍師都係咁諗！"},{"pid":"a8e6b2f442b7bbb3b0f40c318747859b4d5e0040","tid":1722420,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:54:20.000Z","msg":"大家要思考識得用「拉」<br />\n唔好比5毛警犬佔領連登"},{"pid":"41e59c1f30f7060374345c6357a68c96ec926c72","tid":1722420,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd10f85dd84a64d3f8173a6ca66df7f8012c8f69","tid":1722420,"uid":69271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:43:36.000Z","msg":"建議睇邊度？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:55:59.000Z","msg":"建議理性思考 多包容<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">友善提醒 虛心接納 </span></span>"},{"pid":"7ec2da85ab42b49deaaa342ab81e5e8c4c7e8259","tid":1722420,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:56:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b265340ed7f1cd9fda6aaeefb9c1caeb7ac0dab9","tid":1722420,"uid":83232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:56:35.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"e8c31cd2a6a293e21257da59f6ff54c5b1fcfe63","tid":1722420,"uid":140145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:56:58.000Z","msg":"淨係睇連登神探啲on9推理 夠我笑足成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59908ba65887a2c412c0ebfd78c03866b2329f7","tid":1722420,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:57:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c125b48329841d387ae358f54f99c6156b818705","tid":1722420,"uid":26458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:57:57.000Z","msg":"真 多啲出下街 上少啲連登 個人正面好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog